        -:   92:// C helper for EXACT Non-central T-distribution CDF via Numerical Integration.
        -:   93:// This perfectly replicates R's pt(..., ncp) exactness without requiring complex Beta functions.
        -:   94:static NV exact_pnt(NV t, NV df, NV ncp) {
