        -: 2035:// Bisection algorithm to find the inverse F-distribution (Quantile function)
        -: 2036:// Equivalent to R's qf(p, df1, df2)
        -: 2037:static NV qf_bisection(NV p, NV df1, NV df2) {
        -: 2038:	if (p <= 0.0) return 0.0;
        -: 2039:	if (p >= 1.0) return INFINITY;
